Kazila is a hosting provider that has been in operation since January 2008 (6+ years). We operate out of Texas and offer both virtual and dedicated hosting solutions. 

We are now offering pure SSD Xen-based virtual machines in Dallas, TX.
 
- No overselling/ballooning. 
- We utilize SolusVM as our platform and accept PayPal and credit card. 
- We're running RAID-1 on these SSD nodes. 
- Free weekly backups. 
- 14 day money back guarantee.100% satisfaction or your money back. 

We recently automated our system so expect quick setup and provisioning. We also updated our entire template library due to the Heartbleed bug. 

Our Dallas servers are all housed in zColo (previously Corexchange). Hardware is owned by Kazila and bandwidth is purchased from Incero.  

